text: is a town located in Iburi Subprefecture, Hokkaido, Japan. As of September 2016, the town has an estimated population of 2,665, and a density of 13 persons per km². The total area is 205.04 km². Sōbetsu Town hall ==Notable people from Sōbetsu== *Kitanoumi Toshimitsu, sumo wrestler ==External links== * *Official Website Category:Towns in Hokkaido
